s part of the series of winter quarter events organized as part of ms 40 and the future of feminism speakers carla peterson carla l peterson author and professor of english carla l peterson received her ph d from yale and is professor of english at the university of maryland college park in the american studies association she served on the american quarterly board of managing editors and the board of advisory editors peterson has participated in the tv documentaries ticket to freedom and remembering slavery internationally she has served as a usia academic specialist in donate make a donation social links facebook twitter youtube scribd contact serra house 589 capistrano way stanford ca 94305 8640 map 650 723 1994 gender email stanford edu
